name: structured_v9_cross_loop_generated_step_values_into_list_count
section: cross-compiler-v9
args: a:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Stress cross-feature lowering across control flow, env lookup, runtime collections, predicates, quote/null, and operator dispatch.
law: (= (with [xs (list) i 0] (do (while (< i 3) (begin (set! xs (cons (+ {a} i) xs)) (set! i (+ i 1)))) (count xs))) 3)
